 (419394006), <a href="/web/20180712195908/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0046056&amp;fLockTerm=Fluorodeoxyglucose+F%5e18%5e">Fluorodeoxyglucose F^18^</a>
 (35321007), <a href="/web/20180712195908/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_SNOMEDCT_US_CUI=C0011923&amp;fLockTerm=Imaging">Imaging</a>
