<p>Note: Abbreviations used in the tables are listed at the end of the "Major Recommendations" field.</p>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Variant 2</span>: Pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma. Follow-up post-neoadjuvant therapy. Evaluate resectability for borderline resectable tumor.</strong></p>
<table border="1" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="5" summary="Table: Pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma. Follow-up post-neoadjuvant therapy. Evaluate resectability for borderline resectable tumor.">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th class="Center" valign="top" scope="col">Procedure</th>
            <th class="Center" valign="top" scope="col">Appropriateness Category</th>
            <th class="Center" valign="top" scope="col">Relative Radiation Level</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr>
