<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria. </p></div></p>
                        <h3><a href="#">Guideline Availability</a></h3>
                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Available from the <a href="/web/20180712195908/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=51229&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2facsearch.acr.org%2fdocs%2f3099847%2fNarrative%2f" title="American College of Radiology (ACR) Web site">American College of Radiology (ACR) Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712195908im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>.</p></div></p>
